\c 4
\s Amatshe alitshumi lambili athathwa eJordani abe yisikhumbuzo
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi lapho isizwe sonke sesiqede ukuchapha iJordani, iN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma kuJoshuwa isithi\x + 3.17.\x*:
\v 2 Zithathele amadoda alitshumi lambili ebantwini, indoda ibenye kuleso lalesosizwe\x + 3.12.\x*,
\v 3 uwalaye uthi: Zithatheleni okuvela lapha phakathi kweJordani kuleyondawo, lapho obekumi khona inyawo zabapristi ziqinile\x + 3.13,15.\x*, amatshe alitshumi lambili, liwathwale lichaphe lawo\x + Dute. 27.2.\x*, liwabeke endaweni yokulala lapho elizalala khona ebusuku\x + 4.8,19.\x*.
\v 4 UJoshuwa wasebiza amadoda alitshumi lambili ayewalungisile ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, indoda yabanye kuleso lalesosizwe.
\v 5 UJoshuwa wasesithi kuwo: Dlulani phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, lingene phakathi kweJordani, lizithathele, lowo lalowo, ilitshe elilodwa, \add ale\add*tshate ehlombe, njengokwenani lezizwe zabantwana bakoIsrayeli,
\v 6 ukuze lokhu kube yisiboniso phakathi kwenu. Nxa abantwana benu bebuza kusasa besithi: Ayini lamatshe kini\x + 4.21. Eks. 12.26. Hlab. 44.1.\x*?
\v 7 Lizabatshela-ke: Ngoba amanzi eJordani aqunywa phambi komtshotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd*. Lapho uchapha iJordani, amanzi eJordani aqunywa\x + 3.13,16.\x*. Ngakho lamatshe azakuba yisikhumbuzo ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli kuze kube nininini\x + Eks. 12.14. Nani 16.40.\x*.
\v 8 Labantwana bakoIsrayeli benza njalo njengokulaya kukaJoshuwa, bathatha amatshe alitshumi lambili phakathi kweJordani, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuJoshuwa, ngokwenani lezizwe zabantwana bakoIsrayeli; bawathwala bachapha lawo, baya endaweni lapho abalala khona, bawabeka khona.
\v 9 UJoshuwa wasemisa amatshe alitshumi lambili phakathi kweJordani endaweni lapho inyawo zabapristi ababethwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano ezazimi khona. Njalo asekhona lapho kuze kube lamuhla\x + 4.3.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Ngoba abapristi ababethwele umtshokotsho bema phakathi kweJordani kwaze kwaphela yonke into iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayimlaye yona uJoshuwa ukuyitshela abantu, njengakho konke uMozisi ayekulaye uJoshuwa. Labantu baphangisa bachapha.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi bonke abantu sebeqedile ukuchapha, umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* wachapha, labapristi phambi kwabantu.
\v 12 Njalo abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase bachapha behlomile phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 13.18. Josh. 1.14.\x*, njengokubatshela kukaMozisi\x + Nani 32.27,28.\x*.
\v 13 Phose izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane behlomele impi, bachapha phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ukuya empini, emagcekeni eJeriko.
\v 14 Ngalolosuku iN\nd kosi\nd* yamkhulisa uJoshuwa emehlweni kaIsrayeli wonke, njalo bamesaba njengalokhu babemesaba uMozisi insuku zonke zempilo yakhe\x + 3.7.\x*.
\p
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuJoshuwa isithi:
\v 16 Laya abapristi abathwala umtshokotsho wobufakazi ukuthi bakhuphuke eJordani\x + Eks. 25.16,22.\x*.
\v 17 UJoshuwa wasebalaya abapristi esithi: Khuphukani eJordani.
\v 18 Kwasekusithi lapho abapristi ababethwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* sebekhuphukile phakathi kweJordani, \add l\add*engaphansi yenyawo zabapristi isiphakanyiselwe emhlabathini owomileyo, amanzi eJordani abuyela endaweni yawo, ahamba njengamandulo aphuphuma enkunjini zonke zayo\x + 3.15.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Labantu bakhuphuka besuka eJordani ngolwetshumi lwenyanga yokuqala, bamisa inkamba eGiligali ephethelweni lempumalanga yeJeriko\x + 5.9. Josh. 4.3.\x*.
\v 20 Lalawomatshe alitshumi lambili abawathatha eJordani uJoshuwa wawamisa eGiligali\x + 4.9.\x*.
\v 21 Wakhuluma kubantwana bakoIsrayeli esithi: Nxa abantwana benu bebuza kusasa kuboyise besithi: Ayini lamatshe\x + 4.6.\x*?
\v 22 Lizabazisa-ke abantwana benu lisithi: UIsrayeli wayichapha le iJordani emhlabathini owomileyo\x + 3.17.\x*.
\v 23 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu yenza amanzi eJordani atsha phambi kwenu laze lachapha, njengokwenza kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu kuLwandle oluBomvu eyalomisa phambi kwethu saze sachapha\x + 2.10. Eks. 14.21.\x*,
\v 24 ukuze zonke izizwe zomhlaba zazi isandla seN\nd kosi\x + 1 Kho. 8.42,43. 2 Kho. 19.19. Hlab. 83.18. 106.8.\x*\nd*, ukuthi silamandla\x + Dute. 3.24.\x*, ukuze liyesabe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu zonke izinsuku\x + Eks. 14.31. Dute. 6.2.\x*.
